items.description: Users report being looped back to the login screen after successful FaceID. Correlation with BioSDK v3.4.1 detected. Error: BIO-FAIL-909.
Intermittent failure on Samsung S24 models. Possible TEE (Trusted Execution Environment) timeout.

items.summary: MFA SMS Delivery Delay - UK Carriers
items.description: OTP delivery exceeding 120 seconds. External provider issue (Twilio/Vonage) suspected. Check Monitoring Dashboard for SMS-G7.

items.summary: Session persistence failure after app minimize
items.description: JWT tokens expiring prematurely when app is sent to background. Correlates with new memory management policy in Android 14.

items.summary: App Crash - Root/Jailbreak Detection false positive
items.description: New security update flagging legitimate devices as 'compromised'. Affects RootCheck v2.1 implementation.
